Mr. Beachum.

01:19:31.666 --> 01:19:34.191
Mr. Beachum.

01:19:34.236 --> 01:19:38.104
Uh, Your Honor, um...

01:19:38.140 --> 01:19:40.301
I would like to submit
a motion at this time.

01:19:42.310 --> 01:19:44.642
